      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "さぁ、勇気を振り絞って入って下さい、ご主人様？\nお化け、凄く怖いらしいので気を付けて下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "なんで他人事みたいに……俺一人で行くのか！？\nま、待て、そんなに背中を押さなくても……うおっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.3333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hug-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6166.666666699999,
          "startTime": 24.2666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hug-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6699.999999999999,
          "startTime": 24.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.6985486348
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "い、行ってらっしゃいませー！　ご主人様ー！\nどうか生きて帰って来て下さいね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.9318819682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.5485486348
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.5485486348
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "酷い目にあった……本当に恐ろしかった……\nなかなかスプラッターで……ゆ、夢にまで出てきそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "渚がそばにいてくれたら心強かったんだが……\n結果的に来なくて良かった。あれは刺激が強過ぎる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.0342093026,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.0241043091
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "ホラー映画顔負けの演出と聞いていたので\nその……怖くて、すみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.4907709758,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "気にしなくていいよ。実際スリリングで楽しかったしな\nさぁ、次はどこへ案内してくれるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.1155559858
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、ご主人様も乗ってきましたね\n次は脱出ゲームです。今度は一緒に楽しみましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.9488893192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.6322226525
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.6322226525
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ほ、本格的過ぎる……！！\n脱出に必要な謎解きが全く分からなかったぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.4421096166
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "司会役が芽衣ちゃんだったのも驚きましたね……\nでも芽衣ちゃんがヒントを出してくれなければ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.5421096166,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "永遠に脱出出来なかったかもな。お化け屋敷より怖いな\nしかしなんというか、最近の高校生は凄いんだな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.4520648321
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "飲食系も種類が豊富だし\nグミのプレッツェルに話題のワッフルまであるな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか学園祭というより本当のお祭りみたいだ\nこういうのが今の学生のトレンドなのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.8063056947
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが高校生の時は\nどんなものが流行っていたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.0063056947,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "フルーツが乗った高級かき氷、とかかな？\nそういえば、俺のクラスもやったっけな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.3785283408
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "それも十分本格的じゃないですか。……あ、かき氷！\nせっかくですし、食べに行きましょうか！　さぁさぁ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.3785283408,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_drag-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8721.471659200006,
          "startTime": 143.1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "きゅ、急に引っ張らないでくれ……！　でも、そんなに\nはしゃぐなんて、よっぽど学園祭が楽しみだったんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.7785284362
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんです！　今日は琴乃ちゃんが大事な一歩を\n踏み出せる大切な機会……というのもあるんですが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.2785284362,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "実は私、星見高校に通いたいって思ったのは\n学園祭がきっかけだったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.7451951029,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 168.1118617696
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ、初耳だ\nもし良かったら、詳しく聞いてもいいか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、もちろんです\nあの頃の私は、中学一年生で――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.8232451759,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6000,
          "startTime": 182.8232451759
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数年前、星見高校学園祭",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.0299118999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 182.6232421241
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 182.6232421241
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "（私の父親が、星見高校のOBだったので）\n（その繋がりで、学園祭のチケットをもらったんです）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_12_02-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "（一緒に行きたくて、琴乃ちゃんのことも）\n（誘ったんですけど――）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.2899026873,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
